Not even the General.

525
00:40:50,487 --> 00:40:51,158
Please.

526
00:41:00,647 --> 00:41:03,241
Thank you for the time you've taken.

527
00:41:03,407 --> 00:41:04,476
You're welcome.

528
00:41:07,247 --> 00:41:11,399
Nothing here of interest.
Posting slips, commissary bills.

529
00:41:11,567 --> 00:41:12,761
The routine.

530
00:41:12,927 --> 00:41:14,565
l assumed as much.

531
00:41:14,727 --> 00:41:16,365
lt was to be expected.

532
00:41:20,127 --> 00:41:21,685
You've gone too far!

533
00:41:29,087 --> 00:41:31,920
l do hope this paper
wasn't filed secret defence!

534
00:41:38,047 --> 00:41:40,277
You must tell me if it's important.

535
00:41:40,447 --> 00:41:41,800
lt's nothing.

536
00:41:43,167 --> 00:41:45,078
Just a leave.

537
00:41:45,487 --> 00:41:46,840
From the President?

538
00:41:47,647 --> 00:41:48,762
That's right.

539
00:41:48,967 --> 00:41:50,605
President Poincar
sometimes granted a leave

540
00:41:50,767 --> 00:41:52,246
to a deserving soldier.

541
00:41:53,047 --> 00:41:54,082
End of story!

542
00:41:54,527 --> 00:41:55,926
l'll see you out.

543
00:42:18,047 --> 00:42:19,799
Corporal Bouquet Klber...

544
00:42:20,327 --> 00:42:22,158
Corporal Gaignard Francis...

545
00:42:22,847 --> 00:42:25,042
Private Notre Dame Benot...

546
00:42:25,207 --> 00:42:27,562
Private Bassignano Angel...

547
00:42:27,847 --> 00:42:30,122
Private Langonnet Manech...

548
00:42:30,367 --> 00:42:33,643
For self-mutilation,
you are sentenced to death.

549
